query:
CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `documents` (
  `id` int AUTO_INCREMENT NOT NULL,
  `userId` int NOT NULL,
  `filename` varchar(512) NOT NULL,
  `originalPath` varchar(1024),
  `mimeType` varchar(128),
  `fileSize` int,
  `contentHash` varchar(64) NOT NULL,
  `processingStatus` enum('pending','processing','completed','error') NOT NULL DEFAULT 'pending',
  `processingError` text,
  `totalSections` int DEFAULT 0,
  `totalChunks` int DEFAULT 0,
  `totalEntities` int DEFAULT 0,
  `metadata` text,
  `createdAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  `updatedAt` timestamp NOT NULL DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP ON UPDATE CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  PRIMARY KEY (`id`),
  KEY `documents_contentHash_idx` (`contentHash`),
  KEY `documents_userId_idx` (`userId`),
  CONSTRAINT `documents_userId_fk` FOREIGN KEY (`userId`) REFERENCES `users` (`id`) ON DELETE CASCADE
);
